a68420a44d12"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Create a function that accepts two lists of ",
 StyleBox["CountryData",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "\[CloseCurlyQuote]s properties, and creates a grid of scatter plots for \
every combination of properties."
}], "ItemNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.787687714311097*^9, 3.7876878198889527`*^9}, 
   3.7876878553282123`*^9, {3.7876887503751163`*^9, 3.7876887656238317`*^9}, {
